Introduction

Pharita Chaikong is a Thai singer under YG Entertainment. She is best known as the visual and the lead vocalists of the girl group BABYMONSTER.

On February 29, 2020, Pharita was introduced as a contestant (GI3218) of the Thai survival show "Idol Paradise" under the stage name Bear. She left the show somewhere that same year, before it officially started airing.

On February 1 2023, Pharita was revealed as the sixth member of BABYMONSTER. The group officially debuted on March 31, 2024, with their mini album "BABYMONS7ER".
